{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"98ff8008c9","title":"给非团员们的一封信","origin":"《重庆市右派言论选辑第一集》（内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印），中共重庆市委宣传部办公室编印，1957年8月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"da9b0a5bfd","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":7,"articleId":"98ff8008c9"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"25547bae7f","name":"吕学正"},{"id":"4b20d14954","name":"重庆大学"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9603a0e870","type":"title","text":"给非团员们的一封信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"7235c1c152","type":"authors","text":"重庆大学吕学正","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"c86a742942","type":"paragraph","text":"[编者按：吕学正，重庆大学学生，其家庭犯过五毒。他平时思想言论极为反动。他说：“工人阶级能领导什么？国家应该由小资产阶级来领导，应该是小资产阶级专政”。“他们(指团、班干部)歧视我，我恨他们。假如全世界的人都不爱我，我就要毁灭地球”等。“非团员呼声”是重庆大学鸣放期中，出现的一种反动刊物，其中绝大部分文章，都出自吕的手笔，他在文章中提出取消党、团；建立社会主义青年监督岗；改善非团员低下的处境等三项主张，以反对宗派主义为幌子，迷惑群众，挑拨党群关系，否定党的领导。]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"538b676410","type":"appellation","text":"亲爱的非团员们：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"fa3b5d9de0","type":"paragraph","text":"……团员过组织生活时，我们心里忍不住疼痛……“他们宗派主义孤立我们”，生活确实无情的。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"f36ef12c41","type":"paragraph","text":"地位不平等不单体现在精神和压力方面，还体现在一切权利享受方面，几年来非团员没有留学的，报纸文章上也未歌颂过非团员，就连私人爱情问题也受“宗派关系”带来致命的影响。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"8c43260bea","type":"paragraph","text":"我们认为只要有了集团，那末集团与自由民的矛盾就会有。现在我们要求解散所有党团组织或者根据宪法所给予的权利，让自由民建立志同道合志趣相投的组织。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"94c170d866","type":"paragraph","text":" ——非团员呼声编辑部  6．7．","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"1ee6b2d860","type":"subtitle","text":"为非团员放炮","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"b62f2f0681","type":"paragraph","text":"科学上的伟大创造！","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"88e7468a3b","type":"paragraph","text":"移山倒海的功勋！","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"5cacf6adf9","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"42f2a2a68a","type":"paragraph","text":"那一样离得了我们！！！","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"9d76544a73","type":"paragraph","text":"——年青的非团员","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"7916b3dc49","type":"paragraph","text":"有什么理由","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"649ca46526","type":"paragraph","text":"说“×员比我们先进”！？","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"d150be499a","type":"paragraph","text":"有什么理由","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"35116d5281","type":"paragraph","text":"对我们不信任！！！","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"7cf135b2e8","type":"paragraph","text":"根据宪法第九条？？","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"22e0f1129a","type":"paragraph","text":"出自那一本圣经？？？","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"a0a2226a5c","type":"paragraph","text":"我们愤怒！","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"f48d2df8f4","type":"paragraph","text":"我们呼吁！！","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"ad1d46b85d","type":"paragraph","text":"我们要求真正的平等！！！","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"012dea727e","type":"paragraph","text":"我们不甘心处在最低层。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"0187bd9b5c","type":"paragraph","text":"无论你是作家","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"4f8b8b84d9","type":"paragraph","text":"在作散文……","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"add88d87cc","type":"paragraph","text":"或者诗歌！","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"c4b52a1d2d","type":"paragraph","text":"无论是音乐家","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"d4f6837ab1","type":"paragraph","text":"在作民歌……","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"0c9f914ee9","type":"paragraph","text":"或者进行曲！","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"e6b88aaab9","type":"paragraph","text":"无论你是领导者","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"4bf13fd74c","type":"paragraph","text":"在留学选拔……","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"35cf124149","type":"paragraph","text":"或者毕业分配！","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"04bb82a1ae","type":"paragraph","text":"假设你是正直的，","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"91344214ad","type":"paragraph","text":"真正为了人民","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"4f1a9cf312","type":"paragraph","text":"而不是某个集团！","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"c7c282dd5e","type":"paragraph","text":"你就应该不昧良心！！","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"39ac489488","type":"paragraph","text":"我们有理由要求你","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"0daee796eb","type":"paragraph","text":"冷静！","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"f5288b9421","type":"paragraph","text":"冷静！！","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"},{"id":"e8318f8579","type":"paragraph","text":"再冷静！！！","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"98ff8008c9"}